Write support for zip/tar/bzip2/gzip is implemented.

dependencies.name: SharpYaml
dependencies.description: A YAML portable .NET library. providing parsing and serialization of object graphs, compatible with CoreCLR.

dependencies.name: SharpZipLib
dependencies.description: SharpZipLib (#ziplib, formerly NZipLib) is a compression library for Zip, GZip, BZip2, and Tar written entirely in C# for .NET. It is implemented as an assembly (installable in the GAC), and thus can easily be incorporated into other projects (in any .NET language)
